  "narrative_arc": "Cameroonian immigrant working as a chauffeur for a Lehman Brothers executive during the 2008 financial crisis. Mbue documents two domes collapsing simultaneously — the immigrant family losing their asylum case while the American family loses their wealth. The intersection reveals that both systems — immigration and finance — are equally precarious.",
